    -Application form(University Application Form)
    -Photograph
    -Signature of the Candidate
    -Admit Card of class 12th
    -Marks sheet of 10+2 level
    -Caste Certificate (if applicable)
    -EWS Certificate
    -PWD Certificate
    -Migration Certificate
    -Domocile
    -Aadhar Card or ID Proof
    -Proof of Address
